                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Open /auth and log in with demo@flowwink.com / demo1234. You land in the admin with full access. Start with /admin/leads, /admin/orders, /admin/communications and /admin/approvals — that is where you see autonomous behaviour in context. Then try connecting your own agent via MCP."
